  "body": "### Description\r\nThe following error was reported:\r\n```\r\nteku_1   | Teku is shutting down\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | # A fatal error has been detected by the Java Runtime Environment:\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | #  SIGSEGV (0xb) at pc=0x0000000000000000, pid=1, tid=284\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | # JRE version: OpenJDK Runtime Environment (14.0.2+12) (build 14.0.2+12-46)\r\nteku_1   | # Java VM: OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (14.0.2+12-46, mixed mode, sharing, tiered, compressed oops, g1 gc, linux-amd64)\r\nteku_1   | # Problematic frame:\r\nteku_1   | # C  0x0000000000000000\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | # Core dump will be written. Default location: /opt/teku/core\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | # An error report file with more information is saved as:\r\nteku_1   | # /opt/teku/hs_err_pid1.log\r\nteku_1   | Compiled method (c1) 2705406 17105       3       tech.pegasys.teku.storage.server.rocksdb.core.RocksDbStats$$Lambda$309/0x0000000800f1d040::getAsLong (12 bytes)\r\nteku_1   |  total in heap  [0x00007fe24ccd1490,0x00007fe24ccd1ea8] = 2584\r\nteku_1   |  relocation     [0x00007fe24ccd15e8,0x00007fe24ccd1670] = 136\r\nteku_1   |  main code      [0x00007fe24ccd1680,0x00007fe24ccd1c40] = 1472\r\nteku_1   |  stub code      [0x00007fe24ccd1c40,0x00007fe24ccd1ca0] = 96\r\nteku_1   |  oops           [0x00007fe24ccd1ca0,0x00007fe24ccd1cc0] = 32\r\nteku_1   |  metadata       [0x00007fe24ccd1cc0,0x00007fe24ccd1cf8] = 56\r\nteku_1   |  scopes data    [0x00007fe24ccd1cf8,0x00007fe24ccd1d88] = 144\r\nteku_1   |  scopes pcs     [0x00007fe24ccd1d88,0x00007fe24ccd1e58] = 208\r\nteku_1   |  dependencies   [0x00007fe24ccd1e58,0x00007fe24ccd1e60] = 8\r\nteku_1   |  handler table  [0x00007fe24ccd1e60,0x00007fe24ccd1e90] = 48\r\nteku_1   |  nul chk table  [0x00007fe24ccd1e90,0x00007fe24ccd1ea8] = 24\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | # If you would like to submit a bug report, please visit:\r\nteku_1   | #   https://bugreport.java.com/bugreport/crash.jsp\r\nteku_1   | # The crash happened outside the Java Virtual Machine in native code.\r\nteku_1   | # See problematic frame for where to report the bug.\r\nteku_1   | #\r\nteku_1   | \r\nteku_1   | [error occurred during error reporting (), id 0xb, SIGSEGV (0xb) at pc=0x00007fe26a85a611]\r\nteku_1   | \r\n```\r\n\r\nIt looks like we need to guard against [`RocksDbStats`](https://github.com/PegaSysEng/teku/blob/a170f84a1027cdaf2ffd7ad3483da17bbe85a455/storage/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/storage/server/rocksdb/core/RocksDbInstanceFactory.java#L57) reading from the database after it has been closed.\r\n",
